snippet.title: Bust-A-Move Again [ARCADE] (Very Hard Difficulty, B-E-I-N-T-Z way) - Real-Time Playthrough
snippet.description:
*no savestate
*no slowdown
*no cheats

Играл по правому маршруту: B - E - I - N - T - Z.
